description: Raw video from my new documentary "Passing the Torch." Here, Jimmy Heath reveals his mentor and inspiration, Dizzy Gillespie, and that he's quite pleased that the young musicians at the Tucson Jazz Institute, under the direction of Doug Tidaback, are carrying on the Jazz tradition. To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
title: Jimmy Heath   The Jazz Tradition
